s: Summary: Liquidity Harbour Punk Mixer – a no‑KYC DeFi drinks gathering for protocol rebels and yield farmers.
Topics: permissionless liquidity, on‑chain governance, APY optimization, protocol forking, decentralized community building.
Speakers: UST Web3 Labs founders, BitRush partners, prominent DeFi protocol architects.
r: Connect with underground DeFi innovators shaping next‑gen permissionless finance.
Exchange tactical insights on APY maximization and liquidity bootstrapping.
Forge alliances for cross‑protocol collaborations without regulatory friction.
